    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VRボスとなるか、PCプレイヤーとして史上最大のバトルに参加せよ</h2><br>准备在BOSS FIGHTERS中享受一些狂野的乐趣吧！作为VR玩家，你将成为一个拥有巨大力量的强大Boss，在未来风格的竞技场中大显身手。感受操控环境和与一群狡猾的PC玩家团队战斗的兴奋。如果你在电脑上玩，你需要策略、敏捷和团队协作来击败庞大的Boss。这是一场巨人和战术的碰撞，每一个举动都至关重要。你准备好作为Boss主宰比赛，还是将与他人联手打败这个巨人？加入BOSS FIGHTERS的疯狂战斗世界吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不对称多人战斗</h2>在VR中，扮演Boss角色，你可以自由操控游戏环境，展示你的力量。操纵环境并进行直接战斗，让你在与PC对手的对抗中感受到力量和规模的优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/aa2086d129c012be3c2af3798b70ce81.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/aa2086d129c012be3c2af3798b70ce81.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/aa2086d129c012be3c2af3798b70ce81.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果你在PC团队中，一切都是关于团队合作，快速且聪明地击败巨大的VR Boss。团结起来，制定计划，运用你的技能取得胜利。这是一种融合了脑力和蛮力的有趣混合，非常适合一场刺激的游戏体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/893d474768d89cbee14676fd9d89ee57.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/893d474768d89cbee14676fd9d89ee57.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/893d474768d89cbee14676fd9d89ee57.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器与装备库</h2>作为VR老板，你将获得令人惊叹的、基于物理的武器，它们感觉真实而强大。它们不仅仅很酷，而且具有强大的威力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/1e8e42d58a8248e907d883d128b45587.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/1e8e42d58a8248e907d883d128b45587.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/1e8e42d58a8248e907d883d128b45587.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>而且，如果你是一名PC玩家，有许多酷炫的武器和小工具可供选择<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/09694caeefbc11b1c2490966957fae41.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/09694caeefbc11b1c2490966957fae41.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/09694caeefbc11b1c2490966957fae41.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无论你是在VR中还是在PC上，为充满动感、超级有趣的战斗做好准备。每场战斗都是独特而令人兴奋的，是高辛烷值动作和聪明策略的完美融合！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于物理的战斗和环境互动</h2>体验基于物理的游戏玩法的全新参与水平。作为VR老板，你会感觉自己真的在那里，以最真实的方式在竞技场中玩弄一切。与此同时，PC战斗者会战略性地利用环境在战斗中取得优势。这种基于物理的游戏玩法将一切都带到生活中，使每一次移动和策略都变得非常重要且充满乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/fd1f33b960bdb748ad54d56315b3bf5a.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/fd1f33b960bdb748ad54d56315b3bf5a.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/fd1f33b960bdb748ad54d56315b3bf5a.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >互动式直播和社区参与</h2>BOSS FIGHTERS不仅仅是玩游戏 - 也是关于观看！游戏具有超酷的流媒体功能。因此，如果你在观看，你实际上可以通过影响比赛流程成为行动的一部分。就像你在那里一样，但是在屏幕的舒适度下，使整个事情更加生动和互动。无论你是在游戏中还是在场边欢呼，你都是乐趣的重要组成部分！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/a4a1a08355b05981d444efb439f84b49.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/a4a1a08355b05981d444efb439f84b49.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/a4a1a08355b05981d444efb439f84b49.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >广泛的自定义和进步</h2>在BOSS FIGHTERS中，你可以完全定制你的角色。从各种定制选项中进行搭配。升级你的武器，提升你的能力，在这个酷炫未来主题的角斗士挑战中炫酷地塑造你的角色。重要的是在竞技场中留下你的印记并脱颖而出！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/0c3701e6c56a6ac9c421f8f983b60ecf.poster.avif?t=1748606435\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/0c3701e6c56a6ac9c421f8f983b60ecf.webm?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784650/extras/0c3701e6c56a6ac9c421f8f983b60ecf.mp4?t=1748606435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
